Updating the UAT convention is: 1) find the most recent UAT spreadsheet, and add your entries to there. 2) The next version of UAT will be a copy of the most recent UAT spreadsheet; 3) we archive the second to  last UAT once done into UAT History folder, and keep the last UAT in the Release UAT folder: https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1GO5vux7Ici2H4VhHQos7wnwWf0wulvZV
